Job Description:

Provide administrative support to clinical & research activities, and training course admission & enrollment;
Assist in managing the membership information and records;
Assist in event management and programme promotions; 
Assist in the maintenance of effective record keeping and filing systems;

 Qualification Requirement:

Posses a Bachelor's Degree with at least one year's work experience in NGOs or tertiary institutions; 
Proficiency in PC application, MS Office and Chinese Word Processing
Good command of English and Chinese
Willing to work shifts if necessary, including weekday evenings and Saturdays 

Enthusiastic, detail-oriented and capable of multi-tasking
Good team player and good communication skills
Interested parties, please send your cover letter, full resume with current & expected salary, and availability to us.

 Responsibilities:

Take part in the full IT project lifecycle including requirement gathering, system and data analysis, project execution, user acceptance testing, go-live and documentation,
to ensure project delivery within Scope and schedule for the business;
Work closely with clients to gather requirements and technical details to fully scope out solution, and support function to drive delivery
Prepare test plans, conduct quality assurance test, coordinate UAT (including tracking and fixing) and provide end user training
Create and maintain project documentation including plans, reports, flowcharts and process manuals.

Requirements:


Higher Diploma or Degree holder in Information Technology, Computer Science or relevant discipline;
2 years of experience in assistant business analysis, or business analysis
Strong analytical and problem solving skills;
Diligence and willingness to learn;
Strength in writing project and process documentation;
Strong communication skills in both English and Chinese;
Self-motivated, proactive and able to work under pressure and deadlines;
High potential fresh graduates are welcome to apply. Candidates with less experience will be considered for the position of Assistant Business Analyst.

 Welcome to visit our website Careers (gti.com.hk) for details.
